{
  "_comment": [
    "Raw JSON-RPC bodies captured live from github-mcp-server, used as the",
    "case study for cross-spec-version diff cleanliness. To refresh:",
    "  1. Build github-mcp-server at the relevant go-sdk tag.",
    "  2. For 'new_*' fields, probe stateless server/discover @ 2026-07-28",
    "     with the SEP-2243 headers + reserved _meta. Capture the SSE",
    "     `data:` payload from each method as JSON.",
    "  3. For 'base_*' fields, probe the legacy initialize handshake at",
    "     2025-11-25. Capture the JSON-RPC result envelope as JSON.",
    "  4. Replace any base64 image payloads with the literal string",
    "     '<TRUNCATED>' to keep the fixture small.",
    "These are the *response* shapes; request shapes are documented in",
    "src/probe.ts (buildStatelessReservedMeta + openStatelessHttp/Stdio)."
  ],

  "new_server_discover_response": {
